OL,3,CTrain drivers at 16 rail companies to
OL,4,Cstage fresh wave of strikes
OL,6,FTrain drivers have now not had a pay
OL,7,Frise for five years, since April 2019,
OL,8,Fsaid Aslef
OL,10,Fat 16 rail companies are to stage a
OL,11,Ffresh wave of strikes in April in a
OL,12,Flong-running dispute over pay,
OL,13,Fthreatening more travel chaos for
OL,14,Fpassengers across the country.
OL,16,FMembers of Aslef will hold a rolling
OL,17,Fprogramme of one-day walkouts between
OL,18,FApril 5 and 8, coupled with a six-day
OL,19,Fban on overtime.
