OL,6,FDrivers will strike on Friday April 5
OL,7,Fat Avanti West Coast, East Midlands
OL,8,FRailway, West Midlands Trains, and
OL,9,FCrossCountry, on Saturday April 6 at
OL,10,FChiltern, GWR, LNER, Northern, and
OL,11,FTransPennine, and on Monday April 8 at
OL,12,Fc2c, Greater Anglia, GTR Great
OL,13,FNorthern Thameslink, Southeastern,
OL,14,FSouthern/Gatwick Express, South
OL,15,FWestern Railway main line and depot
OL,16,Fdrivers, and SWR Island Line.
OL,18,FMembers will also refuse to work their
OL,19,Frest days from Thursday, April 4 to
OL,20,FSaturday, April 6 and from Monday,
OL,21,FApril 8 to Tuesday, April 9.
