OL,3,CTrain drivers at 16 rail companies to
OL,4,Cstage fresh wave of strikes
OL,6,FLast month unions announced a renewed
OL,7,Fmandate for industrial action for the
OL,8,Fcoming six months.
OL,10,FAslef general secretary Mick Whelan
OL,11,Fsaid: "Drivers wouldn't vote for
OL,12,Findustrial action, again and again and
OL,13,Fagain, if they thought that was a good
OL,14,Foffer."
OL,16,FHe claims the union has not spoken to
OL,17,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper, his
OL,18,Fdeputy nor the rail minister Huw
OL,19,FMerriman for over four weeks.
